rotational constants. We also calculated the rz(CC) distance to be 1.5312  in 12CH312CD3
by transferring Kuchitsus rz(CH), rz(CD), z(CCH), and z(CCD). We evaluated
the dipole moments of the two species from the Stark effects to be 0.010670.00010 D
