Examinations of the data have led to the following rz structures with standard
errors: For C2H6,rz(CH)=1.09570.002 , rz(CC)=1.53190.002 ,andCCH=111.50.3;
for C2D6, rz(CD)=1.09410.002 , rz(CC)=1.53000.002 ,andCCD=111.40.3;
